    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a noble knight who one night found himself confronted by the devil. The devil offered to grant the knight’s wishes in exchange for joining his army in an attack on the heavens. The knight, however, refused the offer. Enraged, the devil dragged the knight to the underworld. Now, as the knight, you must escape hell, find the devil, and thwart his plans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you'll explore top-down dungeons with semi-randomized levels and engage in action-packed combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find items to survive, such as a boomerang, bow and arrows, and more, to defeat enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect soul crystals to access the boss rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/a4c127943d57994cb09f232fc644bcae.poster.avif?t=1750715697\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/a4c127943d57994cb09f232fc644bcae.webm?t=1750715697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/a4c127943d57994cb09f232fc644bcae.mp4?t=1750715697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/4d5b4d414560489586c48fb078bd6d6f.poster.avif?t=1750715697\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/4d5b4d414560489586c48fb078bd6d6f.webm?t=1750715697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245830/extras/4d5b4d414560489586c48fb078bd6d6f.mp4?t=1